applyMatrix4

(
  • σ
)
Vector3 chainable

Defined in src/davinci-eight/math/Vector3.ts:140

Pre-multiplies the column vector corresponding to this vector by the matrix. The result is applied to this vector. Strictly speaking, this method does not make much sense because the dimensions of the square matrix and column vector don't match. TODO: Used by TubeSimplexGeometry.

Parameters:

  • σ Object

    The 4x4 matrix that pre-multiplies this column vector.

dual

(
  • B
  • changeSign
)
Vector3 chainable

Defined in src/davinci-eight/math/Vector3.ts:684

Constructs a vector which is the dual of the supplied bivector, B. The convention used is dual(m) = I * m. If a sign change is desired from this convention, set the changeSign to true.

Parameters:

  • B SpinorE3
  • changeSign Boolean

Returns:

Vector3:
